data.description: Calling all Investors, first time home buyers or anyone looking to downsize! Welcome to a home that proves good things DO come in small packages! This compact yet highly functional residence is a testament to efficient and thoughtful design. Step into a space where every square foot has been maximized for practicality without compromising on style. There is still room to add your unique touch too! All appliances and riding lawn mower convey so you'll be all set the minute you move in. The cozy but spacious living area offers a comfortable retreat, perfect for relaxation or entertaining guests. The bedrooms offer a peaceful haven designed for restful nights. Embrace the simplicity and ease of maintenance in this smaller but highly functional home. Outside, a large and level, yet manageable yard, ensures outdoor enjoyment without the hassle of extensive upkeep. It even has the footprint to add on to the current home if desired.  If you're looking for a smartly designed and efficient living space, this home is a perfect fit - where small meets functional in a delightful combination. You won't be disappointed! Motivated Seller! Will entertain all offers!
